data.description: ~Motivated seller agrees to pay up to $10,000 toward buyer closing costs or interest rate buy down with an acceptable offer~ If you're looking for a fabulous 4 bedroom POOL home, this is it! Not only is it only 5 years old, but there are almost too many added upgrades to list! With wood-look water resistant laminate flooring throughout the living space, stunning granite counter tops in the kitchen, a completely redone master bathroom including beautiful tile shower and jetted tub, custom barn doors, stone front façade with paver accents widening the driveway, fabulous pool/screen enclosure with solar heating, tankless water heater, and added garage cabinetry, you do not want to miss out on this one! You will love the fully open living space with beautifully upgraded kitchen connecting to the dining and living room. There is true ease of entertaining as the sliding door to the pool area is off the dining area providing easy indoor/outdoor access. The primary suite includes a large en-suite bathroom with walk in shower and separate jetted soaker tub and a huge walk-in closet. The other 3 bedrooms and full bathroom are at the front of the home for a fully split floor plan allowing maximum privacy. There is even hidden storage behind the built-in bookshelf off the kitchen. As you walk outside you will immediately be blown away by the pool and patio area that is covered with a screened enclosure and a fully fenced yard with gates on both sides. Pull down the sun shades, turn on the music and lights, and get ready to enjoy Florida living in this solar heated pool! Not only is this home absolutely beautiful, but the community includes a 24 hour gate for added security and you have easy access to SR 60 to get to I-75 or I-4. Bring your furniture, move right in, and get ready to make this home your own! Schedule a showing today- you do not want to miss out on this one!
